snippet.title: Rosehive Superfoods Holiday Unboxing with Health Coach Amber Bayer!
snippet.description: Chia, Turmeric Spice, and Everything Nice..Welcome to the Holiday Edition of Rosehive Superfoods Box! We’ve carefully curated this selection of superfood samplings as the perfect gift, bursting with 7 goodies and an extra gift valued at $19.99 alone! Watch as Amber unboxes our December box and get ready to discover nutrient-packed superfood snacks, herbs, cooking ingredients and the ultimate Golden Milk {Turmeric Latte} recipe! Peace, Love and Superfoods, friends! Xo
